glass-budget (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Glass Budget
  * Modern glassmorphism UI design
  * Complete budget tracking functionality
  * Account management with multiple account types
  * Transaction tracking and categorization
  * Recurring bill management
  * Savings goals with progress tracking
  * User authentication and security
  * Production-ready packaging for Ubuntu Server
  * Systemd service integration
  * Nginx reverse proxy configuration
  * Automated backup and update scripts

